{"tid":2125082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「選擇性？」警方敷衍放行偷捉野鴿阿伯","createTime":"2020-07-26T02:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T03:08:10.000Z","uid":230104,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"24802195f5cf94f2d69e7156adc1876131da2e74","tid":2125082,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"有動物救援組織近日在其Facebook專頁發文，指有義工在太子目擊一名慣犯捉鴿，上前喝止他並報案。專頁公開了義工與涉事老翁對話的數段影片，片段中老翁承認有捉鴿及將其煮食，惟警方到場後稱沒有看見老翁捉鴿，將他放行。義工批評警方敷衍了事，未有錄取口供便將涉事者放行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200723/FQD5NUWFA4UG25TYRUYRYT2JFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200723%2FFQD5NUWFA4UG25TYRUYRYT2JFY%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=f1273c0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200723%2FFQD5NUWFA4UG25TYRUYRYT2JFY%2F&h=5891788d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200723/FQD5NUWFA4UG25TYRUYRYT2JFY/</a>"},{"pid":"5fc0346a4161f2a348a33d7f37002224f87775ee","tid":2125082,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"香港警曱不嬲都係咁"},{"pid":"c410820363d6a85a4497ed4a12b6dd9c23315c35","tid":2125082,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"195dd0bed084ac8c6538e2f9bfbac288a32620bd","tid":2125082,"uid":129664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:52:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">惟警方到場後稱沒有看見老翁捉鴿，將他放行</span><br />\n<br />\n咁好多罪案警方到場後都見唔到有人犯罪架，咁乜都唔使拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d716297e5a9e6fd28b56fcd46cc412eedd801c9","tid":2125082,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"195dd0bed084ac8c6538e2f9bfbac288a32620bd","tid":2125082,"uid":129664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:52